---
import Base from '@/layouts/Base.astro';
import CTA from '@/components/CTA.astro';
---

<Base title="Miles Sowden | Insurance Executive">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="pt-48 pb-32 max-md:pt-32 max-md:pb-20">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-12 max-lg:px-8 max-md:px-6">
      <h1 class="font-display text-[3.5rem] max-lg:text-5xl max-md:text-[2.5rem] leading-[1.1] tracking-[-0.02em] text-text-primary mb-10 max-w-[900px]">
        Twenty years leading Australian insurers through growth and transformation
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl max-md:text-lg leading-relaxed text-text-secondary mb-12 max-w-[720px]">
        I have led businesses with more than $1 billion in premium and teams of 700 people across five major financial institutions. From navigating the Royal Commission to deploying artificial intelligence at scale, I build the strategy, teams and culture that deliver lasting performance.
      </p>
      <div class="flex gap-4 flex-wrap max-md:flex-col">
        <CTA href="/contact" external={false}>
          Contact
        </CTA>
        <CTA href="#work-and-impact" variant="secondary" external={false}>
          Work and impact
        </CTA>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What I bring -->
  <section class="py-32 max-md:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-12 max-lg:px-8 max-md:px-6">
      <h2 class="font-display text-[2.5rem] max-md:text-[2rem] leading-[1.2] tracking-[-0.02em] text-text-primary">
        What I bring
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl max-md:text-lg leading-relaxed text-text-secondary mt-6 max-w-[720px]">
        Strategic and operational leadership across the full scope of insurance and financial services.
      </p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 max-md:grid-cols-1 gap-x-16 gap-y-12 mt-16">
        <div class="border-t-[3px] border-text-accent pt-8">
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl leading-[1.3] text-text-primary mb-3">Strategic Leadership</h3>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">Setting direction for boards and executive teams. Defining where to compete, how to win and what to stop doing.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-t-[3px] border-text-accent pt-8">
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl leading-[1.3] text-text-primary mb-3">Business Transformation</h3>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">Turning around underperforming businesses through pricing, product modernisation, digital channels and operational discipline.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-t-[3px] border-text-accent pt-8">
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl leading-[1.3] text-text-primary mb-3">People and Culture</h3>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">Building high-performing, accountable teams through clear strategy, capability development and cultural alignment.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-t-[3px] border-text-accent pt-8">
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl leading-[1.3] text-text-primary mb-3">Technology and AI</h3>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">Deploying data, digital and artificial intelligence as strategic assets to drive customer outcomes and competitive advantage.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Work and impact -->
  <section class="py-32 max-md:py-20" id="work-and-impact">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-12 max-lg:px-8 max-md:px-6">
      <h2 class="font-display text-[2.5rem] max-md:text-[2rem] leading-[1.2] tracking-[-0.02em] text-text-primary">
        Work and impact
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl max-md:text-lg leading-relaxed text-text-secondary mt-6">
        Two decades of outcomes across major Australian financial institutions, including through the Royal Commission, record catastrophe seasons, mergers and regulatory reform.
      </p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 max-md:grid-cols-1 gap-8 mt-16">
        <div class="p-10 max-md:p-8 bg-bg-card">
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl leading-[1.3] text-text-primary mb-4">Strata Community Insurance</h3>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">General Manager, Data and Technology Solutions. Deployed digital channels, pricing sophistication and AI automation. Cleared a backlog of 30,000 tasks, reduced underwriting cycle time by 19% and achieved 76% staff engagement.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-10 max-md:p-8 bg-bg-card">
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl leading-[1.3] text-text-primary mb-4">Commonwealth Bank</h3>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">General Manager, General Insurance. Led a $1 billion insurer with 700 staff serving one million customers. Developed a rating factor that reduced premiums by 10% while improving the loss ratio by 1%. Grew digital sales from 20% to 70%.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-10 max-md:p-8 bg-bg-card">
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl leading-[1.3] text-text-primary mb-4">Hollard Insurance</h3>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">Chief Revenue Officer. Established a 15-year strategic alliance with Commonwealth Bank for one million customers. Led the transition and portfolio transformation to meet target returns and risk appetite.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-10 max-md:p-8 bg-bg-card">
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl leading-[1.3] text-text-primary mb-4">Westpac Banking Corporation</h3>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">Senior Manager. Established distribution plan and operating model for the Westpac-Allianz alliance. Doubled written premiums and increased NPS from +25 to +44.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Closing -->
  <section class="py-32 max-md:py-20 bg-bg-dark text-white">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-12 max-lg:px-8 max-md:px-6">
      <p class="text-xl max-md:text-lg leading-relaxed text-white/90 max-w-[720px]">
        I have spent twenty years building, transforming and leading insurance businesses. If that experience is relevant to what you are working on, I would welcome a conversation.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-12">
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-10 py-4 text-base font-medium no-underline rounded-lg transition-all duration-200 bg-text-accent text-white border-[1.5px] border-text-accent hover:bg-[#B36F4F] hover:border-[#B36F4F]">
          Contact
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
